text: Abdelali Lahrichi (born 19 July 1993) is a Moroccan professional basketball player. He represented Morocco's national basketball team at the 2017 AfroBasket in Tunisia and Senegal, where he recorded most steals for Morocco.Morocco – FIBA Afrobasket 2017, FIBA.com, Retrieved 31 August 2017. ==References== ==External links== * FIBA profile * Real GM profile * Afrobasket.com profile Category:1993 births Category:AS Salé (basketball) players Category:Living people Category:Moroccan men's basketball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Shooting guards Category:Small forwards Category:Sportspeople from Casablanca
